keyword:
	keyword: Rush
	match: RSH
	mode: official
	reminder: This Digimon can attack the turn it was played.
	
keyword:
	keyword: Blitz
	match: BLZ
	mode: official
	reminder: If your opponent has 1 or more memory, you can attack with this Digimon.

keyword:
	keyword: Raid
	match: RAID
	mode: official
	reminder: When this Digimon attacks, you may switch the target of attack to 1 of your opponent's unsuspended Digimon with the highest DP.
	
keyword:
	keyword: Evade
	match: EVADE
	mode: official
	reminder: If this Digimon would be deleted, you may suspend it to prevent that deletion.